'''New Calamar''', also known as '''Camalar''', was a [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Esseles's southern continent|southern continent]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Esseles/Legends|Esseles]]. It was named for the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] of Esseles, [[Calamar]]. New Calamar was the location of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire's]] [[Terril Naval Base]].

When the [[Jatz/Legends|Jatz]] musician [[Fitz Roi]] performed in Camalar, he wore the clothes of a [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]], which nearly led to his sponsor, [[Flangth-2-Go]], ending their sponsorship.

